data.description: Open House Cancelled - Welcome to modern elegance in this less than 1-year-old home! Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this residence is a perfect blend of style and functionality. The spacious, open-concept living areas are adorned with quartz countertops, offering a touch of luxury throughout. Enjoy the convenience of a 3-car garage and a flat backyard, perfect for entertaining or relaxation. Skip the wait for new construction—this home is move-in ready, providing a contemporary living experience without the wait. Don't miss the chance to make this stylish haven your own!
